Social Media Privacy Policy
The protection of your personal data is very important to us. In the following, you will find information on how we handle your data, which are recorded through your use of our social media presence on social networks and platforms.
Summary
magicplan extends its social media presence to other platforms such as Twitter, Instagram, Facebook, Circle (magicplan Community platform), YouTube, and LinkedIn, with each provider responsible for data processing on their respective platforms. The policy informs users about general data processing on social media platforms, emphasizing market research, advertising, contact, and contract handling. The policy outlines users' rights in the transfer of data and provides information on the duration of data storage, concluding with a list of links to the privacy policies of the mentioned social media providers. The information provided is current as of April 2022.
