magicplan Privacy Policies
An overview of magicplan's privacy policies.
At magicplan, we prioritize transparency and data protection. We have several privacy policies to inform our users about the handling of their data in various scenarios.
Privacy Policy for the App magicplan
This policy focuses on data processing within our mobile application. It covers technical communication data, tracking, registration, processing of orders, and app permissions. For a comprehensive understanding, please review the full policy
here
.
Privacy Policy for the Website magicplan.app
This policy focuses on data protection concerning our website, magicplan.app. It encompasses information on data collection, usage, and storage practices. For a comprehensive understanding of how we handle your data, please review the full policy
here.
Information on Data Protection regarding the Processing of Customer and Prospect Data
This policy details how we process personal data from our customers. It covers the types of information collected, the purposes for processing, and the legal basis. For a comprehensive understanding of how we handle your data, please review the full policy
here
.
Social Media Privacy Policy
Our Social Media Privacy Policy outlines how we manage data collected through our social media channels. It explains the information we gather, the purposes behind it, and guides users on managing their privacy settings. For a comprehensive understanding, please review the full policy
here
.
Data Protection Information For Applicants
If you are applying to join our team, our Data Protection Information For Applicants policy explains how your data is processed during the hiring process. It includes information on the legal basis, categories of personal data, sources of data, and data storage duration. Find out more
here
.
By providing these policies, we aim to ensure that our users clearly understand how their data is handled across various interactions and platforms at magicplan.
Learn more about our
Information & Security
and
Terms of Service
policies.
